title: Chinese: VSTS Realworld
eventShortDescription: ​Dipping your toes in Visual Studio Team System isn't easy; you just don't know where to start. VSTS Realworld is designed to guide you through this learning curve with a series of real-world scenarios, covering requirements, architecture design, development, testing and build. This session lets you experience a software life cycle on Team Foundation Server and understand how to implement the process in your own team.
